"drop them under :guilabel:`Filters`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Filters` khusus dan menyusunnya "
"menggunakan :guilabel:`Separators`, buka tab :guilabel:`+ Add` dan tarik "
"serta lepas di bawah :guilabel:`Filters`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:101
msgid ""
"To add an existing field under the search dropdown menu, go to "
"the :guilabel:`+ Add` tab and drag and drop it "
"under :guilabel:`Autocompletion Fields`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan field yang sudah ada di bawah menu dropdown pencarian, "
"buka tab :guilabel:`+ Add` dan tarik serta lepas di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Autocompletion Fields`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Project model's Search view on the Kanban view"
msgstr "Tampilan Search model Project pada tampilan Kanban"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:112
