msgstr "Lebih dari satu record view"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:121
msgid "Kanban"
msgstr "Kanban"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:123
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Kanban` :icon:`oi-view-kanban` view is often used to support "
"business flows by moving records across stages or as an alternative way to "
"display records inside *cards*."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`Kanban` :icon:`oi-view-kanban` sering digunakan untuk "
"mendukung alur bisnis dengan memindahkan record melintasi tahapan atau "
"sebagai cara alternatif untuk menampilkan record di dalam *kartu*."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:127
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Kanban` view exists, it is used by default to display data "
"on mobile devices instead of the :ref:`List view <studio/views/multiple-"
"records/list>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika tampilan :guilabel:`Kanban` ada, tampilan ini digunakan secara default "
"untuk menampilkan data pada perangkat mobile alih-alih :ref:`tampilan List "
"<studio/views/multiple-records/list>`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:130
msgid ""
"To prevent users from creating new records, untick :guilabel:`Can Create`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencegah pengguna membuat record baru, hapus centang :guilabel:`Can "
"Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:131
msgid ""
"To create records directly within the view, in a minimalistic form, "
"enable :guilabel:`Quick Create`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat record langsung dalam tampilan, dalam form minimalis, "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Quick Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:133
#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:160
msgid ""
"To set a default grouping for records, select a field "
"under :guilabel:`Default Group By`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur pengelompokan default untuk record, pilih field di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Default Group By`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Project model's Kanban view"
msgstr "Tampilan Kanban model Project"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:143
msgid "List"
msgstr "Daftar"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:145
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`List` :icon:`oi-view-list` view is used to overview many "
"records at once, look for records, and edit simple records."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`List` :icon:`oi-view-list` digunakan untuk melihat "
"banyak record sekaligus, mencari record, dan mengedit record sederhana."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:148
msgid ""
"To prevent users from creating, editing, deleting or duplicating records, "
"untick :guilabel:`Can Create`, :guilabel:`Can Edit`, :guilabel:`Can Delete`, "
"or :guilabel:`Can Duplicate`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencegah pengguna membuat, mengedit, menghapus atau menduplikasi "
"record, hapus centang :guilabel:`Can Create`, :guilabel:`Can "
"Edit`, :guilabel:`Can Delete`, atau :guilabel:`Can Duplicate`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:150
msgid ""
"To create and edit records directly within the view, select "
"either :guilabel:`Add record at the bottom`, :guilabel:`Add record on top` "
"or :guilabel:`Open form view` under :guilabel:`When Creating Record`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat dan mengedit record langsung dalam tampilan, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Add record at the bottom`, :guilabel:`Add record on top` "
"atau :guilabel:`Open form view` di bawah :guilabel:`When Creating Record`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:155
msgid ""
"This prevents users from opening records in :ref:`Form view <studio/views/"
"general/form>` from the :guilabel:`List` view."
msgstr ""
"Ini mencegah pengguna membuka record dalam tampilan :ref:`Form <studio/views/"
"general/form>` dari tampilan :guilabel:`List`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:158
msgid "To edit several records at once, tick :guilabel:`Enable Mass Editing`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit beberapa record sekaligus, centang :guilabel:`Enable Mass "
"Editing`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:159
msgid ""
"To change the way records are sorted by default, select a field "
"under :guilabel:`Sort By`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah cara record diurutkan secara default, pilih field di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Sort By`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:161
msgid ""
"To add a button, click :guilabel:`Add a button` at the top of the list, "
"enter a :guilabel:`Label`, and select the button's action:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan tombol, klik :guilabel:`Add a button` di bagian atas "
"daftar, masukkan :guilabel:`Label`, dan pilih tindakan tombol:"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:168
msgid ""
"The widths of columns in a :guilabel:`List` :icon:`oi-view-list` view are "
"computed automatically to provide the optimal user experience. However, it "
"is also possible to set a fixed column width per field. To do so, click on "
"the relevant column to open the field's :icon:`fa-"
"server` :guilabel:`Properties` tab, then enter the desired number of pixels "
"in the :guilabel:`Column Width (px)` field."
msgstr ""
"Lebar kolom dalam tampilan :guilabel:`List` :icon:`oi-view-list` dihitung "
"secara otomatis untuk memberikan pengalaman pengguna yang optimal. Namun, "
"dimungkinkan juga untuk mengatur lebar kolom tetap per field. Untuk "
"melakukannya, klik kolom yang relevan untuk membuka tab :icon:`fa-"
"server` :guilabel:`Properties` field tersebut, lalu masukkan jumlah piksel "
"yang diinginkan di field :guilabel:`Column Width (px)`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:175
msgid ""
"To add a :icon:`oi-draggable` (:guilabel:`drag handle`) icon to reorder "
"records manually, add an :ref:`Integer field <studio/fields/simple-fields-"
"integer>` with the :guilabel:`Handle` widget."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan ikon :icon:`oi-draggable` (:guilabel:`drag handle`) untuk "
"mengurutkan record secara manual, tambahkan :ref:`field Integer <studio/"
"fields/simple-fields-integer>` dengan widget :guilabel:`Handle`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Drag handle icon enabling to sort records manually in List view"
msgstr ""
"Ikon drag handle yang memungkinkan untuk mengurutkan record secara manual "
"dalam tampilan List"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Sales order model's List view"
msgstr "Tampilan List model sales order"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:190
msgid "Map"
msgstr "Peta"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:192
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Map` :icon:`fa-map-marker` view is used to display records on "
"a map. For example, it is used in the Field Service app to plan an itinerary "
"between different tasks."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`Map` :icon:`fa-map-marker` digunakan untuk menampilkan "
"record pada peta. Misalnya, ini digunakan dalam aplikasi Layanan Lapangan "
"untuk merencanakan rute perjalanan antara tugas yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:196
msgid ""
"A :ref:`Many2One field <studio/fields/relational-fields-many2one>` linked to "
"the *Contact* model is required to activate the view, as the contact address "
"is used to position records on the map."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Field Many2One <studio/fields/relational-fields-many2one>` yang "
"terhubung ke model *Contact* diperlukan untuk mengaktifkan tampilan, karena "
"alamat kontak digunakan untuk memposisikan record pada peta."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:199
msgid ""
"To select which kind of contact should be used on the map, select it "
"under :guilabel:`Contact Field`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih jenis kontak mana yang harus digunakan pada peta, pilih di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Contact Field`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:201
msgid ""
"To hide the name or the address of the record, tick :guilabel:`Hide Name` "
"or :guilabel:`Hide Address`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyembunyikan nama atau alamat record, centang :guilabel:`Hide Name` "
"atau :guilabel:`Hide Address`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:203
msgid ""
"To add information from other fields, select them "
"under :guilabel:`Additional Fields`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan informasi dari field lain, pilih di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Additional Fields`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:204
msgid ""
"To have a route suggested between the different records, "
"tick :guilabel:`Enable Routing` and select which field should be used to "
"sort records for the routing."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendapatkan rute yang disarankan antara record yang berbeda, "
"centang :guilabel:`Enable Routing` dan pilih field mana yang harus digunakan "
"untuk mengurutkan record untuk rute tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Task model's Map view"
msgstr "Tampilan Map model Task"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:215
msgid "Timeline views"
msgstr "Timeline views"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:218
msgid ""
"When you first activate one of the timeline views, you need to select "
"which :ref:`Date <studio/fields/simple-fields-date>` or :ref:`Date & Time "
"<studio/fields/simple-fields-date-time>` fields on your model should be used "
"to define when the records start and stop in order to display them on the "
"view. You can modify the :guilabel:`Start Date Field` and :guilabel:`Stop "
"Date Field` after activating the view."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda pertama kali mengaktifkan salah satu tampilan timeline, Anda "
"perlu memilih bidang :ref:`Date <studio/fields/simple-fields-date>` "
"atau :ref:`Date & Time <studio/fields/simple-fields-date-time>` mana pada "
"model Anda yang harus digunakan untuk menentukan kapan catatan dimulai dan "
"berhenti agar dapat ditampilkan pada tampilan. Anda dapat "
"mengubah :guilabel:`Start Date Field` dan :guilabel:`Stop Date Field` "
"setelah mengaktifkan tampilan."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:229
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Kalender"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:231
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Calendar` :icon:`fa-calendar` view is used to overview and "
"manage records inside a calendar."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`Kalender` :icon:`fa-calendar` digunakan untuk melihat "
"dan mengelola catatan di dalam kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:234
msgid ""
"To create records directly within the view instead of opening the :ref:`Form "
"view <studio/views/general/form>`, enable :guilabel:`Quick Create`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat catatan langsung di dalam tampilan alih-alih "
"membuka :ref:`tampilan Form <studio/views/general/form>`, "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Quick Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:238
msgid ""
"This only works on specific models that can be *quick-created* using only a "
"*name*. However, most models do not support quick creation and open "
"the :guilabel:`Form` view to fill in the required fields."
msgstr ""
"Ini hanya bekerja pada model tertentu yang dapat *dibuat cepat* hanya "
"menggunakan *nama*. Namun, sebagian besar model tidak mendukung pembuatan "
"cepat dan membuka tampilan :guilabel:`Form` untuk mengisi bidang yang "
"diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:242
msgid ""
"To color records on the calendar, select a field under :guilabel:`Color`. "
"All the records sharing the same value for that field are displayed using "
"the same color."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mewarnai catatan pada kalender, pilih bidang di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Color`. Semua catatan yang memiliki nilai yang sama untuk "
"bidang tersebut ditampilkan menggunakan warna yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:246
msgid ""
"As the number of colors is limited, the same color can end up being assigned "
"to different values."
msgstr ""
"Karena jumlah warna terbatas, warna yang sama dapat berakhir ditugaskan ke "
"nilai yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:249
msgid ""
"To display events lasting the whole day at the top of the calendar, select "
"a :ref:`Checkbox field <studio/fields/simple-fields-checkbox>` that "
"specifies if the event lasts the whole day."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan acara yang berlangsung sepanjang hari di bagian atas "
"kalender, pilih :ref:`bidang Checkbox <studio/fields/simple-fields-"
"checkbox>` yang menentukan apakah acara berlangsung sepanjang hari."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:252
msgid ""
"To choose the default time scale used to display events, "
"select :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, "
"or :guilabel:`Year` under :guilabel:`Default Display Mode`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih skala waktu default yang digunakan untuk menampilkan acara, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Year` di bawah :guilabel:`Default Display Mode`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:256
msgid ""
"You can also use a :guilabel:`Delay Field` to display the duration of the "
"event in hours by selecting a :ref:`Decimal <studio/fields/simple-fields-"
"decimal>` or :ref:`Integer <studio/fields/simple-fields-integer>` field on "
"the model which specifies the duration of the event. However, if you set "
"an :guilabel:`End Date Field`, the :guilabel:`Delay Field` will not be taken "
"into account."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menggunakan :guilabel:`Delay Field` untuk menampilkan durasi "
"acara dalam jam dengan memilih bidang :ref:`Decimal <studio/fields/simple-"
"fields-decimal>` atau :ref:`Integer <studio/fields/simple-fields-integer>` "
"pada model yang menentukan durasi acara. Namun, jika Anda "
"mengatur :guilabel:`End Date Field`, :guilabel:`Delay Field` tidak akan "
"diperhitungkan."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Calendar Event model's Calendar view"
msgstr "Tampilan Kalender model Calendar Event"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:270
msgid "Cohort"
msgstr "Cohort"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:272
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cohort` :icon:`oi-view-cohort` view is used to examine the "
"life cycle of records over a time period. For example, it is used in the "
"Subscriptions app to view the subscriptions' retention rate."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`Cohort` :icon:`oi-view-cohort` digunakan untuk memeriksa "
"siklus hidup catatan selama periode waktu. Misalnya, ini digunakan dalam "
"aplikasi Langganan untuk melihat tingkat retensi langganan."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:276
msgid ""
"To display a measure (i.e., the aggregated value of a given field) by "
"default on the view, select a :guilabel:`Measure Field`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan ukuran (yaitu, nilai agregat dari bidang tertentu) secara "
"default pada tampilan, pilih :guilabel:`Measure Field`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:278
msgid ""
"To choose which time interval is used by default to group results, "
"select :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, "
"or :guilabel:`Year` under :guilabel:`Interval`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih interval waktu mana yang digunakan secara default untuk "
"mengelompokkan hasil, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Year` di bawah :guilabel:`Interval`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:280
msgid ""
"To change the cohort :guilabel:`Mode`, select "
"either :guilabel:`Retention` :dfn:`the percentage of records staying over a "
"period of time, it starts at 100% and decreases with time` "
"or :guilabel:`Churn` :dfn:`the percentage of records moving out over a "
"period of time - it starts at 0% and increases with time`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah :guilabel:`Mode` cohort, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Retention` :dfn:`persentase catatan yang bertahan selama "
"periode waktu, dimulai pada 100% dan menurun seiring waktu` "
"atau :guilabel:`Churn` :dfn:`persentase catatan yang keluar selama periode "
"waktu - dimulai pada 0% dan meningkat seiring waktu`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:284
msgid ""
"To change the way the :guilabel:`Timeline` (i.e., the columns) progresses, "
"select either :guilabel:`Forward` (from 0 to +15) or :guilabel:`Backward` "
"(from -15 to 0). For most purposes, the :guilabel:`Forward` timeline is used."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah cara :guilabel:`Timeline` (yaitu, kolom) berkembang, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Forward` (dari 0 hingga +15) atau :guilabel:`Backward` "
"(dari -15 hingga 0). Untuk sebagian besar tujuan, "
"timeline :guilabel:`Forward` digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Subscription model's Cohort view"
msgstr "Tampilan Cohort model Subscription"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:296
msgid "Gantt"
msgstr "Gantt"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:298
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Gantt` :icon:`fa-tasks` view is used to forecast and examine "
"the overall progress of records. Records are represented by a bar under a "
"time scale."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`Gantt` :icon:`fa-tasks` digunakan untuk meramalkan dan "
"memeriksa kemajuan keseluruhan catatan. Catatan diwakili oleh batang di "
"bawah skala waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:301
msgid ""
"To prevent users from creating or editing records, untick :guilabel:`Can "
"Create` or :guilabel:`Can Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencegah pengguna membuat atau mengedit catatan, hapus "
"centang :guilabel:`Can Create` atau :guilabel:`Can Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:303
msgid ""
"To fill cells in gray whenever a record should not be created there (e.g., "
"on weekends for employees), tick :guilabel:`Display Unavailability`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengisi sel dengan warna abu-abu kapan pun catatan tidak boleh dibuat "
"di sana (misalnya, pada akhir pekan untuk karyawan), "
"centang :guilabel:`Display Unavailability`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:307
msgid ""
"The underlying model must support this feature, and support for it cannot be "
"added using Studio. It is supported for the Project, Time Off, Planning, and "
"Manufacturing apps."
msgstr ""
"Model yang mendasari harus mendukung fitur ini, dan dukungan untuk itu tidak "
"dapat ditambahkan menggunakan Studio. Ini didukung untuk aplikasi Project, "
"Cuti, Perencanaan, dan Manufaktur."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:310
msgid "To show a total row at the bottom, tick :guilabel:`Display Total row`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan baris total di bagian bawah, centang :guilabel:`Display "
"Total row`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:311
msgid ""
"To collapse multiple records in a single row, tick :guilabel:`Collapse First "
"Level`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menciutkan beberapa rekaman dalam satu baris, "
"centang :guilabel:`Collapse First Level`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:312
msgid ""
"To choose which way records are grouped by default on rows (e.g., per "
"employee or project), select a field under :guilabel:`Default Group by`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih cara pengelompokan rekaman secara default pada baris "
"(misalnya, per karyawan atau project), pilih field di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Default Group by`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:314
msgid ""
"To define a default time scale to view records, "
"select :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, "
"or :guilabel:`Year` under :guilabel:`Default Scale`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menentukan skala waktu default untuk melihat rekaman, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Year` di bawah :guilabel:`Default Scale`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:316
msgid ""
"To color records on the view, select a field under :guilabel:`Color`. All "
"the records sharing the same value for that field are displayed using the "
"same color."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mewarnai rekaman pada tampilan, pilih field di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Color`. Semua rekaman yang memiliki nilai sama untuk field "
"tersebut ditampilkan menggunakan warna yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:320
msgid ""
"As the number of colors is limited, the same color can be assigned to "
"different values."
msgstr ""
"Karena jumlah warna terbatas, warna yang sama dapat ditetapkan untuk nilai "
"yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:322
msgid ""
"To specify with which degree of precision each time scale should be divided "
"by, select :guilabel:`Quarter Hour`, :guilabel:`Half Hour`, "
"or :guilabel:`Hour` under :guilabel:`Day Precision`, :guilabel:`Half Day` "
"or :guilabel:`Day` under :guilabel:`Week Precision`, and :guilabel:`Month "
"Precision`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menentukan tingkat presisi pembagian setiap skala waktu, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Quarter Hour`, :guilabel:`Half Hour`, atau :guilabel:`Hour` "
"di bawah :guilabel:`Day Precision`, :guilabel:`Half Day` "
"atau :guilabel:`Day` di bawah :guilabel:`Week Precision`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Month Precision`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Planning Shift model's Gantt view"
msgstr "Tampilan Gantt model Planning Shift"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:335
msgid "Reporting views"
msgstr "Melaporkan tampilan"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:344
msgid "Pivot"
msgstr "Poros"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:346
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Pivot` :icon:`oi-view-pivot` view is used to explore and "
"analyze the data contained in records in an interactive manner. It is "
"especially useful to aggregate numeric data, create categories, and drill "
"down the data by expanding and collapsing different levels of data."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`Pivot` :icon:`oi-view-pivot` digunakan untuk menjelajahi "
"dan menganalisis data yang terdapat dalam rekaman secara interaktif. "
"Tampilan ini sangat berguna untuk menggabungkan data numerik, membuat "
"kategori, dan merinci data dengan memperluas dan menciutkan tingkat data "
"yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:350
msgid ""
"To access all records whose data is aggregated under a cell, "
"tick :guilabel:`Access records from cell`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses semua rekaman yang datanya digabungkan di bawah sel, "
"centang :guilabel:`Access records from cell`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:352
msgid ""
"To divide the data into different categories, select field(s) "
"under :guilabel:`Column grouping`, :guilabel:`Row grouping - First level`, "
"or :guilabel:`Row grouping - Second level`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membagi data ke dalam kategori yang berbeda, pilih field di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Column grouping`, :guilabel:`Row grouping - First level`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Row grouping - Second level`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:354
msgid ""
"To add different types of data to be measured using the view, select a field "
"under :guilabel:`Measures`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan berbagai jenis data yang akan diukur menggunakan tampilan, "
"pilih field di bawah :guilabel:`Measures`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:356
msgid ""
"To display a count of records that made up the aggregated data in a cell, "
"tick :guilabel:`Display count`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan jumlah rekaman yang membentuk data agregat dalam sel, "
"centang :guilabel:`Display count`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Purchase Report model's Pivot view"
msgstr "Tampilan Pivot model Purchase Report"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:367
msgid "Graph"
msgstr "Grafik"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:369
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Graph` :icon:`fa-area-chart` view is used to showcase data "
"from records in a bar, line, or pie chart."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan :guilabel:`Graph` :icon:`fa-area-chart` digunakan untuk menampilkan "
"data dari rekaman dalam bentuk grafik batang, garis, atau pie."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:372
msgid ""
"To change the default chart, select :guilabel:`Bar`, :guilabel:`Line`, "
"or :guilabel:`Pie` under :guilabel:`Type`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah grafik default, pilih :guilabel:`Bar`, :guilabel:`Line`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Pie` di bawah :guilabel:`Type`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:374
msgid ""
"To choose a default data dimension (category), select a field "
"under :guilabel:`First dimension` and, if needed, another "
"under :guilabel:`Second dimension`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih dimensi data default (kategori), pilih field di "
"bawah :guilabel:`First dimension` dan, jika diperlukan, pilih field lain di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Second dimension`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:376
msgid ""
"To select a default type of data to be measured using the view, select a "
"field under :guilabel:`Measure`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih jenis data default yang akan diukur menggunakan tampilan, "
"pilih field di bawah :guilabel:`Measure`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:378
msgid ""
"*For Bar and Line charts only*: To sort the different data categories by "
"their value, select :guilabel:`Ascending` (from lowest to highest value) "
"or :guilabel:`Descending` (from highest to lowest) under :guilabel:`Sorting`."
msgstr ""
"*Khusus untuk grafik Bar dan Line*: Untuk mengurutkan kategori data yang "
"berbeda berdasarkan nilainya, pilih :guilabel:`Ascending` (dari nilai "
"terendah ke tertinggi) atau :guilabel:`Descending` (dari tertinggi ke "
"terendah) di bawah :guilabel:`Sorting`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:381
msgid ""
"*For Bar and Pie charts only*: To access all records whose data is "
"aggregated under a data category on the chart, tick :guilabel:`Access "
"records from graph`."
msgstr ""
"*Khusus untuk grafik Bar dan Pie*: Untuk mengakses semua rekaman yang "
"datanya digabungkan di bawah kategori data pada grafik, "
"centang :guilabel:`Access records from graph`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:383
msgid ""
"*For Bar charts only*: When using two data dimensions (categories), display "
"the two columns on top of each other by default by "
"ticking :guilabel:`Stacked graph`."
msgstr ""
"*Khusus untuk grafik Batang*: Saat menggunakan dua dimensi data (kategori), "
"tampilkan dua kolom bertumpuk secara default dengan "
"mencentang :guilabel:`Stacked graph`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/views.rst:0
msgid "Sales Analysis Report model's Bar chart on Graph view"
msgstr "Grafik Batang model Laporan Analisis Penjualan pada tampilan Grafik"

